{meta: title Beyond The Shadow Of A Doubt}
{meta: artist Jim Reeves}
{meta: composer Ted Daffan and Theda Daffan}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]You are my guiding [C]star
[G]The one love I can't live [D7]without
[G]All these things I know you [C]are
[D7]Beyond the shadow of a [G]doubt
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[C]Through rain through snow or storm
[G]The coldest darkest hour [D7]out
[G]Your love will keep me [C]warm
[D7]Beyond the shadow of a [G]doubt
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[C]No gates no bars my dear
[G]Will ever serve to keep me [D7]out
[G]Call my name and I'll be [C]there
[D7]Beyond the shadow of a [G]doubt
{end_of_verse}
